OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Warning lights flash' as  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore workers seek help     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The "warning lights are flashing red"  
OL,6, as the number of people in work seeking
OL,7, crisis support has more than doubled in
OL,8, two years, according to a charity.     
OL,10,FCitizens Advice says it referred 6,983 
OL,11,Femployed people for crisis support     
OL,12,Fbetween July and September this year.  
OL,14,FThat compares with 2,780 people in the 
OL,15,Fsame period in 2020.                   
OL,17,FThe latest figures come as the cost of 
OL,18,Fliving is rising at the fastest rate   
OL,19,Ffor 40 years.                          
